E_D("replace into `news` values('12','Member Handbook [会员手册]','Updated: November 12, 2013 Version Number: 1.01<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrading Hours :<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBeijing : 10:00 - 22:00 ( Monday to Friday )<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFirst, membership management<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1, the following persons shall not apply to members :<br />\r\n1 ) under 18 years of age and persons over the age of 65 ;<br />\r\n2 ) no civil capacity or with limited capacity for civil conduct of the parties ;<br />\r\n3 ) full-time students ;<br />\r\n4 )<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> regular employees of the enterprise ;</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	Second, members of the business management<br />\r\nCompany pursuant to the [International Electronic Commerce Regulations], the relevant law [ prohibiting pyramid schemes ], etc. , rules and regulations related to the company . Member companies engaged in marketing activities is strictly prohibited , without the government approved business projects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 , General Provisions<br />\r\nStrict compliance with national laws and policies ;<br />\r\nStrict compliance with the companys rules and regulations ;<br />\r\nStrictly follow the voluntary , fair, honest and trustworthy principle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2 , business promotion management<br />\r\nMember violates these provisions , the title will be processed and investigated recommend people responsible.<br />\r\n1 ) prohibited any violation of law or immoral conduct e-commerce business ;<br />\r\n2 ) non- flaunt personal wealth , income or exaggerated propaganda personal enjoyment ;<br />\r\n3 ) non- forcing others to engage in e- business, should fully respect the customers choice ;<br />\r\n4 ) non- distorted relationship between members and the company ;<br />\r\n5 ) in any form is prohibited harm the interests of the company or other direct sellers ;<br />\r\n6 ) in any form is prohibited discredit the company , employees and customers ;<br />\r\n7 ) is strictly prohibited denigrate other company, brand , product, occupation or trade ;<br />\r\n8 ) non- malicious grab team ;<br />\r\n9 ) is strictly prohibited conduct e-commerce business by involving politics , religion , etc. ;<br />\r\n10 ) The name of the company is prohibited to participate in or organize illegal gatherings.<br />\r\n11 ) is prohibited by a public place , the network (QQ group , the Forum ) released to conduct business ;<br />\r\n12 ) non- cross-level contact , each allowing only responsible for their own recommendation and the referrer ;<br />\r\n13 ) prohibited the sale of real estate, debt Member ;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3 , Other<br />\r\n1 ) Member companies should be required to attend training on time , get the appropriate legal knowledge , business, etc. ;<br />\r\n2 ) members shall be designated by the use of text , audio and video electronic data to carry out business activities ; may not be used or sold without the approval of the company s information ;<br />\r\n3 ) without the Company s authorization , the member may not be copied or printed text produced by the company , audio-visual materials and other works ;<br />\r\n4 ) without the written authorization of the company , the member shall not use the name and trademark of the company;<br />\r\n5 ) Members shall not be registered trademarks or company name as any other institution or product names ;<br />\r\n6 ) Members shall not hold any form of training sessions or activities.<br />\r\n7 ) members shall be self-managed account password , self- dealing transactions , accounts and funds to ensure safety .<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4 , supervision and punishment<br />\r\n( 1 ) Member found himself rights have been infringed may submit a request to the request processing company ( escalation by the referee ) , but the company did not apply to the company within three months from the date the violation occurred no longer accepted ;<br />\r\n( 2 ) members of the company in violation of laws or regulations, or conduct prejudicial to the reputation of the company s products or corporate image, the company is entitled to the seriousness and other factors , member -by-case decision on punishment according to relevant provisions of the way the company , including but not limited to, oral and written warned for violating the code of conduct appropriate to freeze membership account , even immediate cancellation of membership , etc. ;<br />\r\n( 3 ) members of the company disagrees with the decision , it should be made from the date of the decision in the company for 30 days , in writing, to review the application , otherwise it will lose the right to apply for review . During the review, the original sanction decided to continue in force ;<br />\r\n( 4 ) disputes between members , by the members of the common burden of proof ;<br />\r\n( 5 ) In the course of doing business , such as the member for violation of the Code of laws, regulations and plans, the operating system and endanger the interests of the company s Articles , the Company reserves and claims shall be held .<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5, the company reserves the right to interpret and amend the powers of the manual.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	更新日期: 2013年11月12日 &nbsp;版本号: 1.01<br />\r\n<br />\r\n交易时间:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n北京时间: &nbsp; 10:00 -22:00 (周一到周五)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一、会员资格管理<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1、下列人员不得申请为会员：<br />\r\n1）未满18周岁及65岁以上的人士；<br />\r\n2）无民事行为能力或者限制民事行为能力的人士；<br />\r\n3）全日制在校学生；<br />\r\n4）本企业的正式员工；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n二、会员业务管理<br />\r\n公司根据《国际电子商务管理条例》，《禁止传销条例》等相关法律、法规和公司相关规章。公司严厉禁止会员从事传销活动、在未经政府核准的经营项目。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1、总则<br />\r\n严格遵守国家的法律、政策；<br />\r\n严格遵守公司的规章、制度；<br />\r\n严格遵循自愿、公平、公正、诚实守信原则。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2、业务推广管理<br />\r\n会员违反以下规定，将予以封号处理，并追究推荐人责任。<br />\r\n1) 严禁以任何违反法律或不道德的行为开展电子商务业务；<br />\r\n2) 严禁炫耀个人财富，夸大经济收入或宣导个人享受；<br />\r\n3) 严禁强迫他人从事电子业务，应当充分尊重顾客的选择；<br />\r\n4) 严禁歪曲会员和公司的关系；<br />\r\n5) 严禁以任何形式损害公司或其他直销员的利益；<br />\r\n6) 严禁以任何形式诋毁公司、员工及顾客；<br />\r\n7) 严禁诋毁其他的公司、品牌、产品、职业或行业；<br />\r\n8) 严禁恶意抢团队；<br />\r\n9) 严禁通过涉及政治、宗教信仰等方式开展电子商务业务；<br />\r\n10)严禁以公司的名义参加或组织非法聚会。<br />\r\n11)严禁通过公众场合、网络（QQ群、论坛）发布开展业务；<br />\r\n12)严禁跨级联系，每人仅允许负责各自的推荐人及被推荐人；<br />\r\n13)严禁变卖房产、举债加入会员；<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3、其他<br />\r\n1）会员应当按时参加公司规定的培训，获得相应的法律、业务等知识；<br />\r\n2） 会员应当使用公司指定的文字、音像电子资料开展业务活动；不得使用或销售未经公司核准的资料；<br />\r\n3）未经公司授权，会员不得复制或印刷公司制作的文字，视听资料等作品；<br />\r\n4）未经公司书面授权，会员不得使用公司的名称和商标；<br />\r\n5）会员不得以公司名称或其注册商标作为其他任何机构或产品的名称；<br />\r\n6）会员不得举办任何形式的培训会议或活动。<br />\r\n7）会员应当自行管理账号密码，自行买卖交易，保证账户及资金安全。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4、监督与处分<br />\r\n(1) 会员发现其本人权益受到侵害，可以向公司(由推荐人逐级上报)提出要求处理的请求，但自侵权行为发生之日起三个月内未向公司提出申请的公司不再受理；<br />\r\n(2) 会员违反法律法规或者公司规定，或者行为有损公司产品声誉或公司企业形象，公司有权按情节轻重及其他因素，逐案依据公司相关规定决定对会员的处分方式，包括但不限于口头和书面告诫，因违反守则行为相应冻结会员户头，甚至立即取消会员资格等；<br />\r\n(3) 会员对于公司处理决定有异议的，应当在公司处理决定做出之日起30天内，书面提出复查申请，否则将失去申请复查的权利。在复查期间，原处分决定继续生效；<br />\r\n(4) 会员之间发生纠纷的，由会员共同承担举证责任；<br />\r\n(5) 在开展业务的过程中，如会员因违反法律、法规及公司制定的各项守则、制度和营运细则而危害公司利益的，公司保留依法追究和索赔。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5、公司保留本手册的解释权及修改权。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','CN55500','2013-12-13 09:49:15','0','1','0');");
